WEBVTT

00:00:01.440 --> 00:00:04.040
The world needs bridges.

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:09.040
Have you ever thought about
what it would be like not to have any?

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:13.016
It's hard to imagine
a civilization without bridges

00:00:13.040 --> 00:00:14.416
because they're so essential

00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:17.176
for growth and development
of human society,

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:21.120
but they're not just about a safe way
across a river or an obstacle.

00:00:23.720 --> 00:00:26.976
They shout about connectivity --

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:28.200
community.

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:30.856
They reveal something about creativity,